    "text": "Inspector General Recommendation Transparency Act of 2017\n\nThis bill amends the Inspector General Act of 1978 to require the Council of Inspectors General on Integrity and Efficiency to establish and operate a public database of open Inspector General recommendations on which corrective action has not been completed within one year of issuance."
